{"tid":1975942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實有玩開戰略game都會明點解歐盟會奶共","createTime":"2020-04-17T01:39:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T12:42:26.000Z","uid":47268,"like":17,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"737492f0a2fd8cdc8b2547e297808e4ef6e5fe8e","tid":1975942,"uid":47268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T01:39:38.000Z","msg":"首先錢唔錢都係其次<br />\n<br />\n先唔理共產黨做咗幾多仆街野<br />\n<br />\n一個國家想要發圍<br />\n<br />\n最主要當然係聯合較弱既一方去一齊對抗最強勢嗰面<br />\n<br />\n呢家局勢明顯美帝點都勁支共幾皮<br />\n<br />\n如果你想自己國家崛起係咪應該聯合支共打鳩美國再從中取利啦<br />\n<br />\n特別係歐洲嗰幾個列強<br />\n<br />\n會唔會甘心再做下把位落去<br />\n<br />\n俄佬呢啲機會主義者就睇住兩邊黎食"},{"pid":"b3da5a873905914aa73ec9b841ef7e1009d82ee1","tid":1975942,"uid":47268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T01:39:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"22b5797474f8a128c5b2830ac3dfbf71eaad05f2","tid":1975942,"uid":47268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T01:42:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"71112648ecab903ef8a05d48b3273d38697f1edd","tid":1975942,"uid":194326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T01:44:22.000Z","msg":"點解釋歐洲瘋狂泵水落WHO"},{"pid":"1cffa24b8c52724d0aa5bef32ebc173c783c7e0a","tid":1975942,"uid":47268,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"71112648ecab903ef8a05d48b3273d38697f1edd","tid":1975942,"uid":194326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T01:44:22.000Z","msg":"點解釋歐洲瘋狂泵水落WHO"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T01:51:33.000Z","msg":"On9囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebde37eea1e4bd821eb165c823ffdc3bf1d29d83","tid":1975942,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T01:52:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3684d54df1627deca4502e037e2388b6cd12d1be","tid":1975942,"uid":155983,"like":2,"dislike":16,"score":-14,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T01:54:55.000Z","msg":"其實中美都係好仆街，不過美就一路都